{"Id":583096,"Title":"谕俗诗","Dynasty":"明","Author":"钟芳","Context":"惟兹临漳，闽南奥区。紫阳故治，流风宛如。我来贰政，夕惕怀惭。进汝庶民，恳谕再三。汝耕汝渔，汝乐汝土。敬汝宗祀，孝汝父母。兄弟同胞，勿戕以夷。勿听妇言，和乐怡怡。睦族洽邻，乃俭乃勤。恭上敬长，保富安贫。勿嫉善良，勿暴寡弱。宁死勿为，盗贼赌博。盗贼杀身，赌博败家。善恶之报，毫釐不差。汝能积善，焉用祷神。如其不善，鬼神勿歆。慎勿轻生，斗讼赴狱。宁甘退逊，终远耻辱。常怀一忍，可致千祥。小事不忍，卒罹祸殃。惟酒与色，伤生败德。节之谨之，知止自足。惟货与利，引凶招祟。谨之制之，勿彊分外。凡我庶民，我言不诬。铭在汝心，求遵圣谟。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"5b02a5508430d8e0e80cb9451419cb34","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6486093,"Sentence":"惟兹临漳，闽南奥区。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi cǐ lǐn zhāng ，min nā ào ōu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486094,"Sentence":"紫阳故治，流风宛如。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi yáng gù zhì ，lǐu fēng wǎn rú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486095,"Sentence":"我来贰政，夕惕怀惭。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ lái èr zhèng ，xī tì huái cán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486096,"Sentence":"进汝庶民，恳谕再三。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jìn rǔ shù mǐn ，kěn yù zài sān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486097,"Sentence":"汝耕汝渔，汝乐汝土。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rǔ gēng rǔ yú ，rǔ lè rǔ tǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486098,"Sentence":"敬汝宗祀，孝汝父母。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jìng rǔ zōng sì ，xiào rǔ fǔ mǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486099,"Sentence":"兄弟同胞，勿戕以夷。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiōng dì tóng bāo ，wù qiāng yi yǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486100,"Sentence":"勿听妇言，和乐怡怡。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wù tīng fù yán ，hé lè yǐ yǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6486101,"Sentence":"睦族洽邻，乃俭乃勤。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mù zú qià lǐn ，nǎi jiǎn nǎi qǐn ","Tag":null,"Ex